# Global safety net for local secrets/artifacts

# Terraform local state and plans
**/.terraform/
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
**/*.tfplan
**/plan.tfplan
**/plan-output.txt
**/crash.log
**/crash.*.log

# Local variable files (may contain account/IP data)
**/terraform.tfvars

# Local SSH keys and cert artifacts
**/*.pem
**/*.key
**/*.p12
**/*.jks
**/*.ppk
**/id_rsa
**/id_rsa.pub

# Local Ansible inventories and vars
**/inventory.ini
**/*.retry
**/host_vars/
**/group_vars/

# Environment files
**/.env
**/.env.*

# OS/editor noise
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.idea/
**/.vscode/
